description: The Suzuki Gixxer (GSX-150) is a 154.9 cc (9.45 cu in) naked motorcycle from Suzuki. The bike was launched in September 2014. Its design is similar to the GSX-S1000. The name derives from a nickname used in Britain and elsewhere for Suzuki's GSX-R series of bikes.
